<h1>荒</h1><p class=neha><span style="color:#990000;">huāng</span><span class=alesi>(huang1)</span> , <span style="color:#009900;">huǎng</span><span class=alesi>(huang3)</span> , <span style="color:#990000;">kāng</span><span class=alesi>(kang1)</span> , <span style="color:#cc7700;">huáng</span><span class=alesi>(huang2)</span> <span class=lesi>// pronunciations of 荒 in Mandarin Pinyin</span></p><h2>Basic information about 荒</h2><div class=abo>
<p><b>Unihan definition:</b> <a href="/dictionary/wasteland" style="color:black;">wasteland</a>, <a href="/dictionary/desert" style="color:black;">desert</a>; <a href="/dictionary/uncultivated" style="color:black;">uncultivated</a></p><p><b>Number of strokes:</b> 9<br><small>Examples of other characters consisting of 9 strokes: <a href="/character/是" title="shi4: indeed, yes, right; to be; demonstrative pronoun, this, that">是</a>, <a href="/character/说" title="shuo1: speak, say, talk; scold, upbraid">说</a>, <a href="/character/要" title="yao4: necessary, essential; necessity">要</a>, <a href="/character/种" title="zhong3: seed; race, breed; to plant">种</a>, <a href="/character/面" title="mian4: face; surface; plane; side, dimension">面</a>, <a href="/character/看" title="kan4: look, see; examine, scrutinize">看</a>, <a href="/character/前" title="qian2: in front, forward; preceding">前</a>, <a href="/character/点" title="dian3: dot, speck, spot; point, degree">点</a>, <a href="/character/将" title="jiang1: will, going to, future; general">将</a>, <a href="/character/很" title="hen3: very, quite, much">很</a></small></p><p><b>Radical:</b> <a href="/character/艸" title="Kangxi radical 140">艸</a>&nbsp;140.6</p><p><b>HSK level:</b> 6 <br><small>Other HSK 6 characters: <a href="/character/横" title="heng2: across">横</a>, <a href="/character/炎" title="yan2: flame, blaze; hot">炎</a>, <a href="/character/孤" title="gu1: orphan, fatherless; solitary">孤</a>, <a href="/character/忠" title="zhong1: loyalty, devotion, fidelity">忠</a>, <a href="/character/尖" title="jian1: sharp, pointed, acute, keen">尖</a>, <a href="/character/泰" title="tai4: great, exalted, superior; big">泰</a>, <a href="/character/裂" title="lie4: split, crack, break open; rend">裂</a>, <a href="/character/胞" title="bao1: womb, placenta, fetal membrane">胞</a>, <a href="/character/捕" title="bu3: arrest, catch, seize">捕</a>, <a href="/character/恰" title="qia4: just, exactly, precisely; proper">恰</a> <a href="/character-list/hsk/level-6" title="List of HSK 6 characters" style="white-space: nowrap;">more hsk 6 charaters &raquo;</a></small></p><p><b>Frequency rank:</b> 1328</p><p><b><a href="/character-list/general-standard" title="Table of General Standard Chinese Characters">General standard</a> index number:</b> 1412</p><p><b>Examples of words containing this character:</b> <a href="/dictionary/备荒" title="bei4 huang1">备荒</a>, <a href="/dictionary/凶荒" title="xiong1 huang1">凶荒</a>, <a href="/dictionary/包荒" title="bao1 huang1">包荒</a>, <a href="/dictionary/丧荒" title="sang1 huang1">丧荒</a>, <a href="/dictionary/垦荒" title="ken3 huang1">垦荒</a>, <a href="/dictionary/抛荒" title="pao1 huang1">抛荒</a>, <a href="/dictionary/拓荒" title="tuo4 huang1">拓荒</a>, <a href="/dictionary/拾荒" title="shi2 huang1">拾荒</a>, <a href="/dictionary/灾荒" title="zai1 huang1">灾荒</a>, <a href="/dictionary/熟荒" title="shu2 huang1">熟荒</a>, <a href="/dictionary/烧荒" title="shao1 huang1">烧荒</a>, <a href="/dictionary/粮荒" title="liang2 huang1">粮荒</a>, <a href="/dictionary/色荒" title="se4 huang1">色荒</a>, <a href="/dictionary/荒僻" title="huang1 pi4">荒僻</a>, <a href="/dictionary/荒原" title="huang1 yuan2">荒原</a>, <a href="/dictionary/荒唐" title="huang1 tang2">荒唐</a>, <a href="/dictionary/荒地" title="huang1 di4">荒地</a>, <a href="/dictionary/荒寒" title="huang1 han2">荒寒</a>, <a href="/dictionary/荒岛" title="huang1 dao3">荒岛</a>, <a href="/dictionary/荒废" title="huang1 fei4">荒废</a>, <a href="/dictionary/荒旱" title="huang1 han4">荒旱</a>, <a href="/dictionary/荒村" title="huang1 cun1">荒村</a>, <a href="/dictionary/荒弃" title="huang1 qi4">荒弃</a>, <a href="/dictionary/荒凉" title="huang1 liang2">荒凉</a>, <a href="/dictionary/荒淫" title="huang1 yin2">荒淫</a></p></div><h2>English translation (based on CEDICT):</h2><div class=ceent><div style="background:#dddddd;float:both;font-family: monospace;">荒[<span style="color:#990000;">huāng</span>]:</div> <div style="float:left;padding-left:15px;">- desolate<br>- shortage<br>- scarce<br>- out of practice<br>- absurd<br>- uncultivated